sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant API
    participant Database

    User->>App: Click "New Note" button
    App->>User: Display note creation form

    User->>App: Fill out note details
    User->>App: Click "Save" button

    App->>API: Send POST request to create note
    API->>Database: Store new note in database
    Database-->>API: Confirmation of note creation
    API-->>App: Success response

    App->>User: Display success message
    App->>User: Update note list with new note
